description: Zore Moshref is a digital kinetic interactive installation artist, NFT artist, NFT Art collector, a creator, art project development, Web & Graphic Designer, an Entrepreneur in the digital media field who was born in 1967 and currently lives in England and works there. She has graduated with M.A in Digital Media Art at the University of Brighton in 2019.At the moment she is focusing her Ph.D. project in the field of Augmented Reality (AR), and Artificial Intelligence (AI).
